<Layout title="The 6-Year Absence Rule: Brisbane Sellers Who Moved Out of Their Main Residence 2026 | Daniel Gierach Property" description="The 6-year absence rule (Section 118-145) lets you keep the main residence CGT exemption while renting out your home for up to 6 years. Here is exactly how it works for Brisbane sellers who moved interstate or overseas." schema={faqSchema}>

